cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper deals with generating videos from captions using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) domains. The use of Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) and 3D spatio-temporal convolutions also suggests the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques such as caption embedding, which could place it under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computational linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories.
